                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Pearson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-02-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 7, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay advises Mr. Pearson that Consul Norton’s special functions ceased when
                    the Department telegraphed to the legation on January 11 that he might return to
                    his post. Instructs him that full compliance with the terms of the settlement
                    must be insisted upon.)</p>
            </div>
